data.description: Unbelievable opportunity! 43.88 +/- acres, multiple structures, multiple options. The property includes a house, 41X50 outbuilding, 2000 sq ft structure that was previously the “The Gunman” business, and more. Seller will pay $10,000 of buyers closing costs. Home has been recently updated w/light bright kitchen. New cabinets, vinyl flooring & paint. Fridge/washer/dryer convey. All bedrooms have private access to bathrooms. Lg covered back patio to enjoy the view. Storm shelter. Water softener. 2 wood burning fireplaces. Office building has multiple spaces, w/ training room/private office/reception area/safe, ½ bath. Could be remodeled for a guest house or multiple uses. Shooting ranges w/additional metal building & structures. Many options in this beautiful property! Both parcels surveyed & copy available. Property “as is”. Rare chance for so many features at this price!
